rk_Test_NBT_required_for_SPU_admission_2024\" title=\"Is National Benchmark Test (NBT) required for SPU admission 2024?\">Is National Benchmark Test (NBT) required for SPU admission 2024?<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p><strong>Table of Contents<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80732219\">About the Sol Plaatje University (SPU) Online Application 2024<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80732220\"><strong>How to Apply for SPU Application 2024<\/strong><\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80732221\">Documents Required for SPU Online Application 2024<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80732222\">SPU Application Fees 2024<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80732223\">Application Deadline:<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80732224\">Applying for Financial Assistance in SPU<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80732225\">Is National Benchmark Test (NBT) required for SPU admission 2024?<\/a><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"about-the-sol-plaatje-university-spu-online-application-form-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"About_the_Sol_Plaatje_University_SPU_Online_Application_Form_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80732219\"><\/a>About the Sol Plaatje University (SPU) Online Application Form 2024<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>This is to inform all and sundry that the management of the Sol Plaatje University(SPU) is inviting applications from interested and suitably qualified students (Indigenes and International) for admission into undergraduate and postgraduate programmes for the 2024 academic year.<\/p>\n<p>Before you apply, see the know the actual programs (Courses) available for the 2024 admission.<\/p>\n<p><a name=\"_Toc80732220\"><\/a><strong>How to Apply for SPU Application 2024<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Visit <a href=\"https:\/\/bit.ly\/3fdrwFs\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a><\/li>\n<li>select Undergraduate\/Postgraduate<\/li>\n<li>Create an Account with your valid email on the portal.<\/li>\n<li>Fill all necessary forms.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"documents-required-for-spu-online-application-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Documents_Required_for_SPU_Online_Application_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80732221\"><\/a>Documents Required for SPU Online Application 2024<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Valid Email<\/li>\n<li>South African Identity Number<\/li>\n<li>Passport Number (International Students)<\/li>\n<li>Final School results<\/li>\n<li>Valid Passport or Identity Document or Birth Certificate<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"spu-application-fees-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"SPU_Application_Fees_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80732222\"><\/a>SPU Application Fees 2024<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Pay a non-refundable application fee of <strong>R100<\/strong> for South African citizens<\/li>\n<li>Pay a non-refundable application fee for foreign citizens of <strong>R100<\/strong><\/li>\n<li>Payments to be made before closing dates<\/li>\n<li>Ensure to use your Person Number or T Number as a reference<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"application-deadline\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Application_Deadline\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80732223\"><\/a>Application Deadline:<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>30 November 2024 <\/strong><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"applying-for-financial-assistance-in-spu\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Applying_for_Financial_Assistance_in_SPU\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80732224\"><\/a>Applying for Financial Assistance in SPU<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Interested applicants can apply for financial assistance (Scholarship) through the NSFAS application <a href=\"https:\/\/www.spu.ac.za\/index.php\/nsfas-2\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">portal<\/a><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"is-national-benchmark-test-nbt-required-for-spu-admission-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Is_National_Benchmark_Test_NBT_required_for_SPU_admission_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80732225\"><\/a>Is National Benchmark Test (NBT) required for SPU admission 2024?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>Yes.<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/bit.ly\/3fdrwFs\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Click here to Apply<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"SPU Online Application Form 2024 for Admission into Sol Plaatje University, SPU Application fees, Programs (Courses), Application Status,&hellip;\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1179,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[12],"tags":[65],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1178"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1178"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1178\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1178"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1178"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=1178"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}